  <Properties>
    <publishDate>
      <Value>2026-03-01T10:30:00</Value>
    </publishDate>
    <summary>
      <Value><![CDATA[Full Council has agreed council tax rates for the 2026 to 2027 financial year. Band D charges rise by 2.99%.]]></Value>
    </summary>
    <main>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p class="govuk-body">At its meeting on 27 February, Full Council voted to set council tax rates for 2026/27. The Band D charge for Greenfield District Council services rises by 2.99%, in line with the government referendum threshold.</p><p class="govuk-body">Bills will be issued in mid-March and the new rates take effect from 1 April. Residents who pay by direct debit don't need to take any action — their installments will be updated automatically.</p>]]></Value>
    </main>
  </Properties>
</Content>
